    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far can you make it? In this challenge based infinite  platformer with dynamic wind system.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the wind pushes against you and changes direction, see how far you can run and how many stages you can finish before you fail or before the moon crosses the horizon and you fail.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292170/extras/c1ccc2a3b2ad9638b85b1bcb1333e596.avif?t=1769512110\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How far can you go?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, jump, chase the Moon, and adapt to changing wind patterns.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silhouette platformer with dynamic wind system that pushes against you or with you in different ways at varied intervals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the wind pushes against you and changes direction, see how far you can run and how many stages you can finish before the moon crosses the horizon.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292170/extras/a32eceae8e7cc711d067118342d163b2.avif?t=1769512110\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Includes 3 separate infinite looping Game Modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Linear Mode: 100 Premade stages consisting of various psychics based obstacles which change in theme every 10 Stages</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Mode: Randomized stages in theme and obstacles</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Legend Mode: 100 Premade Linear stages and progresses into randomized stages after completing the 100th stage</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3292170/extras/f70d3491b01783e090c20560c59100c7.avif?t=1769512110\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the wind pushes against you and changes direction, see how far you can run and how many stages you can finish before the moon crosses the horizon, in this dynamic challenge based platformer.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> <br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
